Episodes.Title: Chapter 1: The Mandalorian
Episodes.Actors: Pedro Pascal, Carl Weathers, Werner Herzog
Episodes.Plot: A Mandalorian bounty hunter tracks a target for a well-paying, mysterious client.

Episodes.Actors: Pedro Pascal, Nick Nolte, Misty Rosas
Episodes.Plot: Target in hand, the Mandalorian must now contend with scavengers.

Episodes.Actors: Pedro Pascal, Werner Herzog, Omid Abtahi
Episodes.Plot: The battered Mandalorian returns to his client for his reward.

Episodes.Actors: Pedro Pascal, Gina Carano, Julia Jones
Episodes.Plot: The Mandalorian teams up with an ex-soldier to protect a farming village from raiders.

Episodes.Actors: Pedro Pascal, Amy Sedaris, Jake Cannavale
Episodes.Plot: On a familiar desert planet, the Mandalorian helps a rookie bounty hunter who is in over his head.

Episodes.Title: Chapter 6: The Prisoner
Episodes.Writer: Christopher L. Yost, Rick Famuyiwa, Jon Favreau
Episodes.Actors: Pedro Pascal, Mark Boone Junior, Bill Burr
Episodes.Plot: The Mandalorian is part of a crew of mercenaries springing a convict from a prison ship.

Episodes.Title: Chapter 7: The Reckoning
Episodes.Actors: Pedro Pascal, Carl Weathers, Gina Carano
Episodes.Plot: An old contact extends an invitation for the Mandalorian to make peace with his enemies.

Episodes.Title: Chapter 8: Redemption
Episodes.Actors: Pedro Pascal, Taika Waititi, Giancarlo Esposito
Episodes.Plot: The Mandalorian and his allies come to know their true enemy, who already knows much about them.
